726945f.text:
Jackson Ave., (background) south side, east of Crane Street, to about Crescent Street, showing overhead the elevated branch of the I.R.T. Subway on 23rd Street.  At the left is shown the N.W. corner of Twenty-sixth and Jackson Aves.
October 16, 1936.
W.F.A. Photo
Federal Art Project.
